    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing tactile engagement and precise gear selection. Crucial enthusiast-grade maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a recent rod bearing service to ensure the longevity of the high-tension rotating assembly. The chassis dynamics are preserved through a factory-spec limited-slip differential and a well-sorted suspension geometry that delivers the communicative steering feedback this platform is renowned for. While the exterior shows the honest patina of a driven machine, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive, making it an ideal candidate for the purist seeking a visceral driving experience.",
