    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 2018 luxury sport sedan has been fastidiously maintained and presents beautifully. Finished in a deep metallic charcoal, the exterior paint retains a mirror-like shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scratch near the fuel door. The vehicle has been garage-kept, which is evident in the preserved condition of the rubber seals and trim. Inside, the cabin is an oasis of comfort; the black leather seats are firm and free of cracks or tears, and the genuine wood accents remain vibrant. Every electronic feature, from the heated steering wheel to the premium 12-speaker sound system, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has undergone oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the most recent multi-point inspection confirmed that the suspension is tight and the cooling system is in top shape. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brake rotors were recently resurfaced for a smooth, vibration-free stop. While there is very light wear on the driver\u2019s entry sill, this car offers a premium driving experience without the premium new-car price tag. Complete service records",
